{"tid":30930,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"輸緊三粒，對面教練話換人","createTime":"2016-12-09T11:18:40.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T13:35:19.000Z","uid":13391,"like":82,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5cf3feb8afca2b1cc27d5f5708b7a25951470f94","tid":30930,"uid":13391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:18:40.000Z","msg":"我哋同對面隊踢波，對面個教練好串，話要炒我哋7個1皮<br />\n<br />\n上半場我哋比人撳住打，話咁快入咗三粒完場<br />\n<br />\n下半場踢咗十分鐘，對面仲未入到第四粒，因為佢哋前面爭波踢<br />\n<br />\n個教練見唔對路，換走咗其中一個前鋒，諗住換個唔獨食兼再勁啲嘅<br />\n<br />\n呢個時候，我見到我哋隊好多人拍撚晒手掌，好似贏咗場波咁<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">而家輸緊三球啊屌你</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"cbc0cfdceedec63b35c26ed79662b6fc6953288b","tid":30930,"uid":7748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:19:56.000Z","msg":"曲到圓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dda3fa8c6fd2b9821a4027b8d007d5fb305b0933","tid":30930,"uid":798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:19:59.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"bb65670e31ccd9767f2b58f26ddd26ac9e845728","tid":30930,"uid":7748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:20:30.000Z","msg":"畀啲豬隊友打下飛機啦"},{"pid":"e43a33cbe59bda76e866744cd02f8b4fe5eae3cc","tid":30930,"uid":12124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:22:14.000Z","msg":"港豬"},{"pid":"34fd97d2758d46b9d437648776b2fc117f69431b","tid":30930,"uid":965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T11:23:56.000Z","msg":"開係波台冇用，個個波台手腳都好心水清<br />\n你開返係cc台屌撚醒佢地好過啦<br />\n波台唔洗d咁低層次既post<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ajv45.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ajv45.jpg&h=35c62225&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b0d08377ba8840f537f004f526c57739fd3803ee","tid":30930,"uid":10397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12